name: ROBQR S1-13
description:
Collection: Minibot Series
Edition: /100
Type: Generative AI illustrations.
Compositions: Concepts, topics, and emergent themes.
Excerpts: eg. Dawn of Singularity, cataclysmic shift in the Anthropocene.
Generation: Ninety-character textual compositions processed with VQGAN and CLIP.
Output: PNG-24 images.
Scale: 1200 x 1200px, 72 DPI.
Format: 16-bit sRGB, iEC61966-2.1 format.
Interpolation: 2xSaI, 4X upscale xBRZ, Affinity Photo.
Color Grading: EnhanceAI, StructureAI and RelightAI, LuminarNeo.
